  "description": "A system is the set of rules and mechanics used to resolve actions in a [role-playing game](../index.md). It provides the procedures that determine what happens when a [character](./character.md) attempts something with an uncertain outcome — how to decide whether an attack hits, whether a negotiation succeeds, or whether a character notices a hidden clue.",
